title: Fetterman, Showing Stroke Effects, Battles Oz in Hostile Senate Debate
description: Lt. Gov. John Fetterman, a Democrat, tried to assure voters of his fitness to serve. Dr. Mehmet Oz, a former celebrity physician and Republican, attacked him as too radical for the job.
dc:creator: Shane Goldmacher
media:description: The Senate race in Pennsylvania between Lt. Gov. John Fetterman and Dr. Mehmet Oz is increasingly seen as a tipping-point contest for control of the chamber.
